OL,3,CActivists who poured fake blood into
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace fountain sentenced
OL,6,FA judge has criticised the "arrogance"
OL,7,Fof animal rights activists who caused
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds worth of damage to
OL,9,Fa Buckingham Palace fountain by
OL,10,Freleasing red dye into it.
OL,12,FLouis McKechnie, 23, Christopher
OL,13,FBennett, 33, Riley Ings, 27, Claire
OL,14,FSmith, 26, and Rachel Steele, 48, of
OL,15,FAnimal Rebellion, were convicted of
OL,16,Fcausing #7,080 of damage to the Queen
OL,17,FVictoria Memorial water feature in
OL,18,FLondon in August 2021.
