OL,3,CActivists who poured fake blood into
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace fountain sentenced
OL,6,FThe dye turned the water red to
OL,7,F"create the impression of a bloodbath"
OL,8,Fand stained the stonework of the Grade
OL,9,FI listed fountain, in front of the
OL,10,Froyal London residence, prosecutors
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FPolice forcibly removed the protesters
OL,14,Fand it took 64 hours to clean the
OL,15,Ffountain.
OL,17,FJudge Gregory Perrins, sentencing at
OL,18,FSouthwark Crown Court on Friday, said
OL,19,Fthe stunt was a "serious act of
OL,20,Fcriminal damage" which had a "high
OL,21,Fdegree" of planning.
