OL,6,FHe said that had the fountain not been
OL,7,Fcleaned quickly and efficiently, there
OL,8,Fwas a "very real risk" that the marble
OL,9,Fstonework would have been "permanently
OL,10,Fdamaged".
OL,12,FThe judge told them: "You were
OL,13,Fconcerned only about promoting your
OL,14,Fcause and thought nothing of the
OL,15,Fconsequences of your actions.
OL,17,F"You each thought that your actions
OL,18,Fwere entirely justified.
