OL,3,CActivists who poured fake blood into
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace fountain sentenced
OL,6,F"Each of you displayed a high degree
OL,7,Fof arrogance that you were completely
OL,8,Fin the right, that your views were all
OL,9,Fthat mattered and that the
OL,10,Fconsequences of your actions were a
OL,11,Fprice worth paying for the promotion
OL,12,Fof your cause."
OL,14,FHe added that they deliberately
OL,15,Ftargeted a "culturally significant"
OL,16,Fmemorial in one of the most prominent
OL,17,Fpositions in London in a "calculated
OL,18,Fattempt" to ensure "maximum
OL,19,Fpublication" for their cause.
