OL,6,FBennett, of Fish Ponds Road, Bristol,
OL,7,FIngs, of no fixed address, McKechnie,
OL,8,Fof Claremont Road, Dorset, Steele, of
OL,9,FCapworth Street, east London, and
OL,10,FSmith, of Chadwick Street, Leeds, all
OL,11,Fdenied criminal damage but were found
OL,12,Fguilty after a trial.
OL,14,FBennett, who appeared via video link
OL,15,Ffrom HMP Peterborough, where he is
OL,16,Fserving a one-and-a-half-year prison
OL,17,Fsentence for causing a public
OL,18,Fnuisance, was handed an 18-month
OL,19,Fsentence to run concurrently with the
OL,20,Fother.
