OL,4,CBuckingham Palace fountain sentenced
OL,6,FThe other four were given 18-month
OL,7,Fjail sentences, suspended for two
OL,8,Fyears. McKechnie, Ings and Smith were
OL,9,Fordered to pay #500 in compensation,
OL,10,Fand Steele #1,000 in compensation.
OL,12,FThe judge singled out "seasoned
OL,13,Fprotester" McKechnie, warning him of a
OL,14,F"severe" prison sentence should he re-
OL,15,Foffend.
OL,17,FHe said: "You have been extremely
OL,18,Ffortunate to have been dealt with
OL,19,Frelatively leniently by the courts in
OL,20,Fthe past."
