OL,6,FLaura Stockdale, defending Steele and
OL,7,FBennett, said her clients were not
OL,8,Finvolved in staining the stonework and
OL,9,Fthat the overall damage was not
OL,10,Fexcessive.
OL,12,FShe told the court that they are no
OL,13,Flonger involved with Animal Rebellion.
OL,15,FShina Animashaun, defending Ings,
OL,16,FMcKechnie and Smith, said his clients
OL,17,Fwere young when the protest happened
OL,18,Fand that there was not a
OL,19,F"sophisticated level" of planning.
